Package: shadow
Type: Package
Title: R Package for Finding Shadow Height and Related Calculations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Dorman", email = "dorman@post.bgu.ac.il", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for calculating shade height given buildings outline, their height, sun azimuth and sun elevation. The package also provides functions for related preliminary calculations: converting polygons to line segments, finding segment azimuth, shifting segments by azimuth and distance.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    sp,
    rgeos,
    raster
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1

